item.title: CWS STANFORD LSU
item.description: Louisiana State players Ryan Theriot, center, Cedrick Harris, left, and Ryan Jorgensen (39) celebrate Saturday, June, 17 2000, after LSU beat Stanford 5-4 in the championship game of the College World Series in Omaha, Neb. (AP Photo/Ted Kirk) AP2000

item.title: APTOPIX Arizona St Alabama Softball
item.description: Alabama's Kelley Montalvo, right, and Charlotte Morgan celebrate their 6-2 win over Arizona State in the NCAA softball championship tournament game in Oklahoma City, Saturday, May 30, 2009. (AP Photo/The Oklahoman, Bryan Terry) AP2009

item.title: Ice Hockey Championship
item.description: 10 APR 2004: Denver University celebrates the only goal of the game by forward Gabe Gauthier (9) against the University of Maine during the Division I Men's Ice Hockey Championship held at the Fleet Center in Boston, MA. Denver defeated Maine 1-0 for the national title. Jamie Schwaberow/NCAA Photos (NCAA Photos via AP Images) NCAAP

item.title: CWS South Carolina Texas
item.description: South Carolina players, rear, watch from their dugout as Texas players celebrate a 12-6 victory to win the College World Series on Saturday, June 22, 2002, in Omaha, Neb. (AP Photo/Nati Harnik) AP2002
